    Model object used at root of team tree. The root is special in several ways:
    • If you click on the root of the tree you get the team summary page, rather than information on any particular group or user
    • If the current user supervises the root group, then the root will be named after that group and will contain everything directly contained by the root group (including users etc.)
    • If the current users does not supervise the root group then the root will be named "My Groups" and will contain all the top level groups supervised or managed by the current user. It will not contain any other entries
